st-name><first-name>Hang-John</first-name><address><city>Taichung City</city><country>TW</country></address></addressbook></inventor></inventors></us-parties></us-bibliographic-data-application><abstract id="abstract"><p id="p-0001" num="0000">A table lamp includes an arm pivotably connected to an adjustment unit located in a base. The adjustment unit has an operation wheel which has a first toothed face. A disk has a second toothed face which is engaged with the first toothed face. A pivot extends through the operation wheel, the disk, the arm, a resilient ring, a washer and the base. When the arm is pivoted, the operation wheel is rotated and the first toothed face moves over the second toothed face while the resilient ring is squeezed. When the first toothed face is engaged with the second toothed face again, the arm is secured again. The arm is pivoted within a recess of the base, and the recess opens between 90 degrees to 110 degrees, the arm can be pivoted to be parallel to the base to save the packing room.</p></abstract></us-patent-application>